1.2
log
@Update to 4.5.5.1
if you need to connect to an old MySQL database (< 5.5) you have to set
$cfg['MysqlMinVersion'] = 50015;
in your config file.
@
text
@$OpenBSD: patch-libraries_common_inc_php,v 1.1 2014/10/15 15:01:14 giovanni Exp $
Force compatibility with MySQL 5.0.x to be able to connect to 
remote databases
